mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="border-left:2.2500pt solid rgb(0,119,182);mso-border-left-alt:2.2500pt solid rgb(0,119,182);padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 7pt ;
